<h1>Health for All Through Primary Care</h1>
<h3 style="margin-top:10px;">Henry Perry</h3>
<p>This course explores why primary health care is central for achieving Health for All. It provides examples of how primary health care has been instrumental in approaching this goal in selected populations and how the principles of primary health care can guide future policies and actions.</p>

