<h2 data-msg="coursera-course-format" class="coursera-course-heading">Course Format</h2>
<div class="coursera-course-detail">There will be one hour of lecture per week with one hour of readings and one hour of discussion. The final exam will consist of an essay that explores the themes and approaches described in the course from the standpoint of the student’s own perspective, locale, or geographic area of interest.</div>

